QuestData.Title: When a Gorm Eats a God
QuestData.Description:
There is nothing more we can do here. I will get Master Sha'lor safely back to Tirna Vaal.
When you get there, report to the droman what we found here.
If the gorm have started to eat the dead wildseeds, and are absorbing the power of the spirits within, we are all in serious danger.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report back to Droman Tashmur in Tirna Vaal.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Report back to Droman Tashmur in Tirna Vaal.
